  • The newest videos (by published date).

item.title: modal - YouTube - Events
item.dc:creator: root
item.content:encoded:
Events

These are videos placed into the 'events' playlist from the ParkourPulse Account.
  • Hand-picked videos for the 'events' playlist.
  • Displays newest first.
It should be noted that this playlist is an effort to bridge the gap between the ages-old arguments of for-or-against competition. This playlist is created to offer something to those who DO enjoy competition within the sport and discipline - an olive branch to try and be inclusive of everyone. This playlist is made to highlight the largest events, jams, competitions and seminars in our community.

Last run at [andyp_scrape_date scrape_id="youtube-events-playlist"].
